            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>)27日09:00股價上漲28元，報375.5元，漲幅8.06%，成交2,923張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為PCB。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲23.23%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.78%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-15,714 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-19,338 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+5,665 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-2,041 張</li> <li>融資增減：+6,171 張</li> <li>融券增減：+192 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
