            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲925.79點至39858.19點，漲幅2.38%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間27日09:00，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲925.79點（或2.38%），暫報39858.19點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+5.78%</li><li>近 1 月：+16.78%</li><li>近 3 月：+21.42%</li><li>近 6 月：+41.41%</li><li>今年以來：+34.42%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>RFIC概念領漲+4.02%。其中    聯發科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)            上漲        9.93%            ;        宏觀(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6568:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6568\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6568-TW</a>)            上漲        7.97%            ;        茂達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6138:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6138\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6138-TW</a>)            上漲        5.85%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>快速充電概念領漲+4.00%。其中    笙泉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3122:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3122\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3122-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        聯發科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)            上漲        9.93%            ;        致新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8081-TW</a>)            上漲        7.64%    。</p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6433149",
